3/ped.xml:[Vedic raśmi. The form &lt;b&gt;raŋsi&lt;/b&gt; is the proper Pali form, originating fr. raśmi through metathesis like amhi for asmi, tamhā for tasmā etc. Cp Geiger &lt;i&gt;P.Gr.&lt;/i&gt; § 50&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;. The form rasmi is a Sanskritism and later]
